{
  "stem": "13096.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was a block made of real beds-- you know, full of full beds.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "In each bed, there were, you know, satin-- satin, you know, covers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Maybe they taken from the trains they arrived, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But it was a luxurious villa, you know, like where we arrive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then the first thing they did, to give us each one box of food by the Red Cross. 5 kilo, or whatever, of food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Jam, and sardines, and this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We couldn't believe our eyes what was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we thought, you know, that is very nice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We can stay there-- we can stay there until the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It's not so bad because there was no work to be done the next day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There were no appel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That lasted, you know, for three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Until we were taken out the idea of the-- of the gas chamber and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So after three days, they took us back again to these horrible blocks with the planks and everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we stayed there, you know, until the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And that is-- but, you know, there was not any more selections because they were already destroyed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "There were nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But you could still die, and you know, that is 25th of January, but you can still die.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You can still die there, but from disease, from cholera, from other diseases.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But we wouldn't be selected anymore for the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But every time we hear-- it wasn't bombed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was blown up with dynamite, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't bombs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was like dynamite.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was-- a camp, you will think it's like a camp, a small camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The camp was very many kilometers.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
